SUB_W13_EVAR_SIUG_ROUTE2_FERRY_000_CUT_0.text:
Well? What have you brought me?
Please say you have copper wire;
I desperately need it for my motors.

SUB_W13_EVAR_SIUG_ROUTE0_DIVING_100_CUT_.text:
You have the right of it, Count.
It wasn't enough to save my village;
I wanted to protect it <i>by my own hand</i>.
